            <h3>State-of-the-Art Facilities</h3>
            <p>Aatura Hospital's ENT Department is equipped with state-of-the-art facilities and advanced technology to support the diagnosis and treatment of ENT conditions. Our outpatient clinics, diagnostic imaging center, audiology lab, and surgical suites are designed to provide a comfortable and efficient environment for patients receiving ENT care.</p>
        </div>
